<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="to-tell-you-the-truth">to tell (you) the truth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[口语] 老实说：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To tell you the truth, I’m very worried about the final examinations next month. 
老实说，我很担心下个月的期末考试。</p></div></div>